<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="figure-n">figure <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'fɪɡə(r)/    美 /'fɪɡjər/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>数字；位数；算术：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the latest <strong>trade figures</strong> 
最新的贸易数据</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have a head for figures</strong>
有算术头脑</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He got a job, earning close to six figures. 
他找到一份工作，收入接近六位数。</p><footer>2013 陕西改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(尤指女性的) 体形 / 身材 / 身影：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a tall figure in black
一个黑衣高个子人影</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Every woman wants a slim figure these days.
如今，每个女性都想拥有苗条的身材。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>人物；人士</strong></h4>
<p>a person who is important or famous：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a public / a <strong>leading</strong> / an authority <strong>figure</strong>
公众/领军/权威人物</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>画像；塑像：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a bronze figure of a horse 
马的铜像</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>图表；图形：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>See Figure 1. 
见图表1。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A triangle is a three-sided figure.
三角形是有三条边的几何图形。</p></div></div>